   "zh": "yn",
   "note": "yes/no token"
  },
  {
   "hash": "12b3b245651bb39b",
   "zh": "「下回再說嘛。」"
  },
  {
   "hash": "8766dcb954b1c412",
   "zh": "「換樣別的嘛？」"
  },
  {
   "hash": "e020ebb2e5fee2a9",
   "zh": "「成啦！」$N給了$Y #7金，收下$0。",
   "note": "成交描述"
  },
  {
   "hash": "e1f0f455e1f9b1d7",
   "zh": "「改主意了嘛？」"
  },
  {
   "hash": "b9cdc0f1c25bf37b",
   "zh": "「俺鋪子開時再來嘛！」",
   "note": "重複句"
  },
  {
